# TypeScript Patterns

## Core Approach

- Interfaces prefixed with `I` (IDataset, ILabel)
- Enums for controlled vocabularies
- Strict typing for API responses

## Reference Implementations

- **Main Types**: `src/types/dataset.ts`

  - Core data structures
  - Enum definitions
  - Status types

- **Label Types**: `src/types/labels.ts`

  - Geospatial annotation types
  - Label classification enums

- **Hook Types**: Check any hook in `src/hooks/`
  - Return type patterns
  - Parameter interfaces

## Key Patterns

- Dataset interface structure from dataset.ts
- Enum usage (IDataAccess, IPlatform, ILicense)
- Form value interfaces from UploadModal.tsx
- API response typing from useDatasets.ts
- Keep enum values concise and readable

## Context Types

- Follow AuthContextType pattern in `src/hooks/useAuthProvider.tsx`
- DataContextType in `src/contexts/DataContext.tsx`
